Ignore Node.js dependencies
This folder is generated by running npm install and can be very large.
node_modules/

Ignore Python virtual environment
This folder is specific to the local machine and can be regenerated.
venv/

Ignore user-uploaded content
We want to keep the folders, but ignore any files inside them.
public/uploads/*
public/processed/*

Use ! to un-ignore a specific file if needed, like a placeholder.
!public/uploads/.gitkeep
!public/processed/.gitkeep

Ignore general log files
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

Ignore environment variables file
This file may contain sensitive keys and should never be committed.
.env

Ignore OS-specific files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

Ignore IDE/editor configuration folders
.vscode/
.idea/